<section class="guide-panel" data-page="echo">
  <header class="panel-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">Echo</span>
    <h2>Sets et priorit&eacute;s de stats</h2>
  </header>

  <div class="echo-shell">
    <div class="echo-sets">
      <article class="echo-set echo-set--best">
        <div class="echo-set__header">
          <div class="echo-set__title">
            <img src="../../assets/img/set/Crown%20of%20Valor.png" alt="Couronne de vaillance" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-choice-label">Choix recommand&eacute;</span>
              <h3>Couronne de vaillance (3p) + Tonnerre du Ciel (2p)</h3>
              <p>
                Son meilleur socle, avec des stacks tr&egrave;s faciles &agrave; garder gr&acirc;ce &agrave; ses boucliers.
                Tu y gagnes surtout <span class="accent-value">ATQ</span>, <span class="accent-value">DGT CRIT</span> et des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts Electro propres.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="echo-item-grid">
          <article class="echo-item echo-item--primary">
            <img src="../../assets/img/echo/The%20False%20Sovereign.png" alt="Souverain apocryphe" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-item__label echo-item__label--primary">&Eacute;cho recommand&eacute;</span>
              <h4>Souverain apocryphe</h4>
              <p>
                Le meilleur choix standard : bonus Electro, bonus d'Attaque lourde et cast tr&egrave;s simple en fin de rotation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="echo-item echo-item--secondary">
            <img src="../../assets/img/set/Lingering%20Tunes.png" alt="R&eacute;sonance sans fin" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-item__label">Alternatives 2p</span>
              <h4>R&eacute;sonance sans fin / Nuages lunaires / Symphonie c&eacute;leste</h4>
              <p>
                Jouables si ton build les demande, mais toujours derri&egrave;re Tonnerre du Ciel en d&eacute;g&acirc;ts purs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="echo-set echo-set--alt">
        <div class="echo-set__header">
          <div class="echo-set__title">
            <img src="../../assets/img/set/Void%20Thunder.png" alt="Tonnerre du Ciel" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-choice-label echo-choice-label--alt">Lecture rapide</span>
              <h3>Pourquoi ce build colle si bien</h3>
              <p>
                Son kit g&eacute;n&egrave;re des boucliers en continu, donc Couronne de vaillance devient chez elle un vrai set DPS.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="echo-item-grid">
          <article class="echo-item">
            <img src="../../assets/img/set/Moonlit%20Clouds.png" alt="Nuages lunaires" />
            <div>
              <span class="echo-item__label">&Agrave; noter</span>
              <h4>Le quickswap reste secondaire</h4>
              <p>
                Augusta aime finir sa rotation d'un bloc. Ne force pas un style quickswap si &ccedil;a casse ton encha&icirc;nement.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <section class="echo-mainstats">
      <div class="echo-mainstats__header">
        <span class="echo-mainstats__kicker">Meilleures stats d'&Eacute;cho</span>
        <h3>Configuration 4 / 3 / 3 / 1 / 1</h3>
        <p>
          Verrouille d'abord le double 3 co&ucirc;t Electro puis ta ligne CRIT. La Recharge reste un confort, pas le coeur du build.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="echo-mainstats__grid">
        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">4 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">Taux CRIT</span>
            <span class="mainstat-sep">&gt;</span>
            <span class="mainstat-alt">DGT CRIT</span>
          </div>
          <p>Choisis surtout selon l'&eacute;quilibre global de ton build.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card mainstat-card--priority">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">3 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">DGT Electro</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le premier 3 co&ucirc;t Electro est la base du build standard.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">3 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">DGT Electro</span>
            <span class="mainstat-sep">&gt;</span>
            <span class="mainstat-alt">ATQ%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le double Electro reste le plus propre. Electro + ATQ% reste jouable si besoin.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">1 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">ATQ%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le premier 1 co&ucirc;t fixe ta base offensive.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="mainstat-card">
          <span class="mainstat-card__slot">1 co&ucirc;t</span>
          <div class="mainstat-card__stats">
            <span class="mainstat-primary">ATQ%</span>
          </div>
          <p>Le second 1 co&ucirc;t ATQ% reste le plus simple et le plus stable.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="echo-substats-divider">
        <span>Substats prioritaires</span>
      </div>

      <div class="substats-grid substats-grid--single">
        <article class="substat-card">
          <h4>Ordre recommand&eacute;</h4>
          <p>
            <span class="accent-text">Recharge</span> jusqu'au confort
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">Taux CRIT</span>
            = <span class="accent-text">DGT CRIT</span>
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">ATQ%</span>
            = <span class="accent-text">DGT Attaque lourde%</span>
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">ATQ</span>
            &gt; <span class="accent-text">DGT Comp&eacute;tence r&eacute;sonatrice%</span>
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>
